ale University</p><p>(19)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwjewqQ5Mj3aRRRRRRDZVOBqiQKpPnJU0_4cK2wTO3y7W5ZIMxGTtuwux436xQ81TL3RyYW5zgQyKBJheBj3F21JdlTMr5G2TZ2LNsNso' target='_blank'>Frequently Asked Questions-Transfer Program</a> &nbsp;Yale University</p><p>(20)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlZWw_8kIptULDSax5hpXVQ7WCxO43btsmlfOpD0ppQs8BtL6hNkkMO-I0zFrThO53mPJorrB4s4Du5yr1W5qk4F6Afl9l75ahw1RulLoAMIflgl75aEV' target='_blank'>Transfer Application Instructions</a>&nbsp;Yale University</p><p>(21)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbyfmLGCeMXy7vp-5hvrsROzlkrdamg4KeiEwtF_yFlhzjtl_YfQXzjr_VWc1c4Lwl93CYHp7SwTgyDeJ7tWyp9QXzjq1nScED4ha_hlqA3' target='_blank'>Majors in Yale College</a> Yale University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h1>研究生申请</h1><p><strong>院系设置</strong></p><p>耶鲁大学共设有15个学院，其中耶鲁学院是本科生院，耶鲁文理学院是研究生院，其余学院均为专业学院（professional school）。耶鲁的暑期课程，面向高三学生开放，主要是一些耶鲁的体验课程，暑期课程开设于耶鲁学院。具体院系设置情况如下：</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:316px">			<p>学院名称</p>			</td>			<td style="width:361px">			<p>学院英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:205px">			<p>成立时间</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:316px">			<p>耶鲁学院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:361px">			<p>Yale College</p>			</td>			<td style="width:205px">			<p>1701</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:316px">			<p>耶鲁文理研究生院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:361px">			<p>Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p>			</td>			<td style="width:205px">			<p>1847</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:316px">			<p>耶鲁<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>建筑学</a>院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:361px">			<p>Yale School of Architecture</p>			</td>			<td style="width:205px">			<p>1972</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:316px">			<p>耶鲁艺术学院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:361px">			<p>Yale School of Art</p>			</td>			<td style="width:205px">		