li></ul><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>机械工程与材料科学系有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>燃烧（Combustion）</li>	<li>流体力学（Fluid Mechanics）</li>	<li>非晶材料（Amorphous Materials）</li>	<li>软物质与复杂流体（Soft Matter &amp; Complex Fluids）</li>	<li>物理与工程生物学（Physical and Engineering Biology）</li>	<li>机器人，机电一体化和人机界面（Robotics, Mechatronics, and Human Machine Interface）</li>	<li>新型材料物理（Physics of Novel Materials）</li>	<li>界面现象（Interfacial Phenomena）</li>	<li>纳米材料（Nanomaterials）*(4)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>课程要求：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbyeTwdft_1Dz777777ipAb5PTjHRQeN1xCvGU0_hl3NhAmHhQnMhASM-5YveX6jhURcLZyPSUnhNt6JSXyveXHJ3fusSUuhstkjO' target='_blank'>Core Course Requirements for the Ph.D. Degree</a></li>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7giLOJkAT-RWywjsBhx6cEOpmnwsz3F3iFOrYZW9EnGT-VH3TDJzXSYQjp2O2_ww0lFk9d4apf1OuOgfhJORiP6wFrUX_980Uiwu-gT3wO4axuYgu-_ltP4I_NcTFa49fPN0Cf-UHn1isBqwm-Efp9fNaUK' target='_blank'>faculty members</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=_r75g1qxLyQ825ogX84hnQ-oeV9lDU1ahu_z2zkoSjFPhBMZda7thMPb2prQBywECNWhpxy-zE7x-M9OO1avntzIo1I4C5SGrfbpy9_SeKD5' target='_blank'>Masters Degrees</a> Yale School of Engineering and Applied Science</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVdik0k8mhXYjjjjjj8QN1ZvQ8naIs0bUchLtd4_r0qygt730CH3REUPNb2LV_6HwINkjEFcqYmgW-m8sbkx0Q_zXJ31oU2HC68JodxCy' target='_blank'>Financial Aid &amp; Tuition</a> Yale School of Engineering and Applied Science</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5awLMS38lNxhO01fJqS0iTl-Jw-dx8HkcPgSyqYRL-8kr-wV8OsIAwfWCJd_MHth-mUyvEDq6IQZ1X-stQ5T1dMKOhIJWkwv' target='_blank'>Graduate Study Admissions</a> Yale School of Engineering and Applied Science</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Hr3vKzAbLk7hGU12333333IDAUIk0fs6Wa7Q-Rw9JK8hgt3GgIMOWf2bviwMcA_4VaGJotkJSyfBUaGJotkJSyfBvxADHxAi' target='_blank'>Rese