>实验<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E6%A0%B8%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>核物理</a>（Experimental Nuclear Physics）</li>	<li>实验<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%B2%92%E5%AD%90%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>粒子物理</a>（Experimental Particle Physics）</li>	<li>引力<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>物理</a>（Gravitational Physics）</li>	<li>高能理论与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>宇宙学</a>（High Energy Theory and Cosmology）</li>	<li>量子电子（Quantum Electronics）</li>	<li>量子信息<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>物理</a>学（Quantum Information Physics (CQuIP)）</li>	<li>理论<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%87%9D%E8%81%9A%E6%80%81%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>凝聚态物理</a>（Theoretical Condensed Matter Physics）</li>	<li>理论<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E6%A0%B8%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>核物理</a>（Theoretical Nuclear Physics）*(3)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>物理系研究涉及到的研究中心与科系：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=srULj0B7LlbvUu3lAEPfHEqCB1hHBlch--RyBdz0-DARJ3XxYS2Tjpi5FI-Kd6QOHOehybVwgqmTtZ2Wet4xWavU8QsKElwnTXjnAvD-K4kWqWjXqZe0zrYle-_Jf4OW6aqcL' target='_blank'>Associated Centers and Departments</a></li>	<li>研究生手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhfpwOBAjPh4OOOOOO9YJBdQW4w7INVI_Z6idXUzAyi2hPokMeCkxcXob0CNkt8XnlL0_o706c1K3jtyzPcTk3jtyzPNHFaLVBjmJjEV8YxdHy9ls' target='_blank'>Student Handbook 2013-2014 Graduate Program in Physics</a>(PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7PgkKhq9VxpKKKKKKyg30RPnWZBGwVr-tS_oN6vu9hL8AwT8g5o8yUI_X4O7sqy-RhaVRJI-LxODsoXVLN8nkKXqeGwFZ' target='_blank'>Tuition &amp; Living Costs</a><a href='https://gsas.yale.edu/admissions/phdmasters-application-process/tuition-funding-living-costs' target='_blank'> </a>Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJ0mkYo9i