）</li>	<li>材料化学（Materials Chemistry）*(9)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Gr-dDkObw4VCAY0zxnCefidGacfnKmvBR8HyQ2NWfvj5HIQMq1dxnRSToJdWwBj6vvUhBoEvoxEWFqwYR' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li>	<li>研究生手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=qrTydP_ALEo5iIDQnnnnn461JbA-H9dlPZPZBDC1yX0lzFMLyYNjibWlP_F-pEW-VIF-BEuLpIeoj4zbhtdvzuvbQ_XlKnhUG_h-HE8AMeFWVroBxeo_DdL2xYR18_X9D0nKlrVlYv-g13GL' target='_blank'>Graduate Student Handbook for Chemistry</a>(PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=CrXRF8CvwlsJdZAxTTTTTT-yWqQeKE6x0joIJh3pLA7GrRfv9H84nVJ4FwOCYwoWY2F1VZ9XgAWThgEg-Vs3uIfd4A-FKQ1Rr1bWy5P' target='_blank'>Tuition &amp; Living Costs</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZioLzABI5Kcddddddbvmc9KYFaH0xQrOLwCtPi0Go89kQdJFfDvVo6ZpRQkpmwC_lQP7qmgbThE6TI7STPjbQV8Kr' target='_blank'>Dates and Deadlines</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=YrwF0vBhwkcdGua3CCCCCCIGrdf4uVGKqVzeAg1v6yScNO9CGz5URvLZuje6mIlCmgkqsaICISALoZVWNwTy3wA7Brp5G9IxGikyN-H' target='_blank'>Required Examinations</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=hrfXwi0PwYZ8xv3aRRRRRR9HLo1IhS2y4XFBUTAyi2hPvkC9vjLovRh6lShXe29B5S9oecAo5zNHeRNH5RNKiRrXlTN95zVEqF17rFMSRlzhA' target='_blank'>Standardized Test Questions</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHNmdLH56-B-7OOOOONQrL7iGj6XtbJbkbkoZZZfm8E9gTj9nPHlQUjxLK3fPHaCqVcw5tQwtPyN-FEuh0ATY7vshE-ml_WJzDwXHg3FBS317VD-VcNZyFN5C4iNCDw2t5OpHUo1JSRZyJehvLNwPogR_oUgOCib6y_pa6P' target='_blank'>Graduate School of Arts and Sciences Programs and Policies 2015&ndash;2016</a> Yale University</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a rel="nof