 target='_blank'>地球化学</a>（Geochemistry）</li>	<li>岩石圈与地表过程（Lithosphere and Surface Processes）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%8F%A4%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>古生物学</a>及进<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>化学</a>（Paleontology, Evolution）</li>	<li>固体<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>地球物理</a>（Solid Earth Geophysics）</li></ul><ul>	<li>太阳与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>地球物理</a>（Program in Solar and Terrestrial Physics (STP)）*(6)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>研究生手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJEnwmHu4jCTaaas88Z2_9PRajXkc-WbQYwJBOwdQnP6C3TJqOm-o_PbROpJd34gqnVaz34df3Z2z34df3Z2z1O05HM0sAdRfXzwBuG5Zjz61Tb_NWmJ7' target='_blank'>GRADUATE PROGRAM HANDBOOK</a>(PDF)</li>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQn8L3NxwvSGGAhsH7r5HlcAZFma8murVpNvtg3ngNjK5h1J519eRDrSU2xYTS3rIyhYd70' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nVWLs_un1QDUUUUUUMElKfyC750sgsWtEpO6mbZApyxO01hACshPcw4pXuWp5OL_4ajif5xMJvQLfRWaOyszmtuAP9q_PXBt63' target='_blank'>Tuition &amp; Living Costs</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Hr3vKzNdwTChv_Y822R9XUfg_tVrs23h4BkEw9coB6TywUiVOOxX_AykWGdP5SoXakSfxa8LJzd5OhCdR2TOGBwCkDvD31F8ZKA4GW' target='_blank'>Dates and Deadlines</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2QLwolVBDiWYvmDowFzqInSr4XdQCbN22B7hG7_lc8CIOca9thMSfdXCmXpCJIzSZFv6U7tBWaeokyqqOyuRbhiOf1VCqkJ0gMz8PGTOs8' target='_blank'>Required Examinations</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aGbfkdft_1k5BBBB5ZZaAo7I-H5Gr0hB4jmVFthf1cFqRcw9PcTfpg