><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>生物与生物医学科学研究生项目设有以下专业方向，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>生物化学、生物物理与结构生物学（Biochemistry, Biophysics, and Structural Biology）</li>	<li>计算生物学与生物信息学（Computational Biology and Bioinformatics）</li>	<li>免疫学（Immunology）</li>	<li>微生物学（Microbiology）</li>	<li>分子细胞生物学、遗传学与发育（Molecular Cell Biology, Genetics, and Development）</li>	<li>分子 医学、药学与生理学（Molecular Medicine, Pharmacology, and Physiology）</li>	<li>神经科学（Neuroscience）*(10)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRv8kyji7MUzPPPPPPLshiU3dE-Aj9x34ppvqk6r75RlB2x5dvo5dk2iZ' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwa1kTXJRmK2xxxxxxuRnIfxh0So76WjQPlBMcX8c9FZyLkYcRrYsCq-iNVKilhz9K562lWBkfdGlvbi1smFsahEfm9QVKH7r19' target='_blank'>Tuition &amp; Living Costs</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Trq48pWvwlsJdZlEggggggc5ARjDXMlLdE_TcAVdNIZLMgH9z87w1GYKehaU4idL4DGMuGpfwPYVBx0JUIuQZIY-5GACuV' target='_blank'>Dates and Deadlines</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=jr4Ascl3wwGN9Tt9XXXXXXJfdwGzQOEtdE_TcAVdNHBFkbIH8Am0CDMI1pBiSUIjSC1ph8RERDgX5gohw-QRu-8xquPlzHyaJdRhpo5' target='_blank'>Required Examinations</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqV8PwYZ8xpgRllllllXFBKw6qzebZ7A9o5W4avr09KXAi7nl8s9l_RB62QGrRgSCNHfD-xhs-RjETc6XTcboIDxpIWLXlTN95zVE9MafXM79eZrAuo' target='_blank'>Standardized Test Questions</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlEFL6UOjEgommmmmqW6y_xMG-NsFIFIrQQeKdSsZjRI1tYMZSbIEjrsfB7OEdSIEgZpd9PyvcrqlcrZCTDX805tIcml-Q9s-Q2f805t3C4-3QwfIQHap08lnQvJz0wfpF5Bn0Osq-0x7Iiq3Mb6WCiG' target='_blank'>Graduate School of Arts and Sciences Pr