rget='_blank'>计算机系统</a>与网络（Computer Systems and Networking）</li>	<li>分布式计算（Distributed Computing）</li>	<li>机器学习（Machine Learning）</li>	<li>编程语言（Programming Languages）</li>	<li>科学计算与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>应用数学</a>（Scientific Computing and Applied Math）</li>	<li>计算机与网络安全（Security and Cryptography）</li>	<li>社会机器人学（Social Robotics）</li>	<li>技术报告（Technical Reports）*(9)</li></ul><p>MS共分三个专业方向，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>未设具体方向（General）</li>	<li>生物信息方向（Bioinformatics）&nbsp;</li>	<li>计算与艺术方向（Computing and the Arts）*(6)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=3rHk7m1ZLDXYcxPTaaaaaLMurj5cOHfTUXBzPHBynMEDCLkBdJk7rXLi0PLi0I1auFK5hP6lr_' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li>	<li>研究生手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=-rGz4Oc9Ln0yNXBVEEEEEHuKeEBvW9MbF54eoJ4Bz8DkM1PWGhP8NhzyqQwTIjWuI9ZdgeCjaIotZwJOckNXZ-D1imF-BEJzglpzfUpFubc9Ty7qkUMuCoMlHea8AZKb2wasbZeM' target='_blank'>Graduate Handbook</a>(PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caJ_wWuxTbesccccccVA5DMklcm1uzCNHPYuTfhRCWA8ViKKFwGKuge_VQ0BVfyS8lz7JinwN2jsO3yc8BekLO9Xrv5xWVX7GoH' target='_blank'>Tuition &amp; Living Costs</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4eRkUBr17dsllllllEhOUpCRjNh3duCOlFPYYhAwSkHvslhiVl3NCKOhVO3hgKDCZ6UM1GloU34OBXqtBeuc2isDp' target='_blank'>Dates and Deadlines</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHN7cw1hiqOV1UUUUUUeZVOBqiQKp62QKCEIhq0YvD8ms6_nl8s9onguogtzZg-7Iw2EvE7yzOVZdC4_1e4_3Q2xsORSAVBH1CLX' target='_blank'>Required Examinations</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=hrfXwiv-LUrJdyF7QyA_jc--UrHt6sjrhgM-rfRLwNCfKcikd-Q23vvtiDhr5WU73o0wNCLZVr16wPCbXVhkm-iCkZT8