ef='http://www.qianmu.org/%E8%AE%A1%E9%87%8F%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>计量经济学</a>（Econometrics）</li>	<li>经济史（Economic History）</li>	<li>经济理论（Economic Theory）</li>	<li>产业组织（Industrial Organization）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93' target='_blank'>国际贸易</a>（International Trade）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>劳动经济学</a>（Labor Economics）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>宏观经济学</a>（Macroeconomics）</li>	<li>政治<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>经济学</a>（Political Economy）</li>	<li>公共<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>经济学</a>（Public Economics）*(8)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_1OktZGdbzmrjFLtN_lpX6bgsG_FaFJB1h1YZ-5-VDHkYrhc-ngHZ3tHCXuIAVRQgE6Kl0r3UZ51aIQWUG2W168' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwaXku1DPCAGffffffSG3SMtEIz5muAYIzs5REBiVZwkN9zyvh1yAx9ZftgPf7IaCBjgO3-kxevc26uWLTIyhH_arwBjGUkK7E1' target='_blank'>Tuition &amp; Living Costs</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=JrvWrUcnkkP-GM4PqqqqqqpH2fVzi5M7TCY1EbKilzp2qBy5RXamr3Q_4PEJc9QAcpbgxP15br-0hVYagF1GEFBi1PWTY7' target='_blank'>Dates and Deadlines</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJ09kltmgolmddddddX9KWI7X392sIgLRumW2a94obmJwvpOXI4yJh_pL2SkLJiprzFvFbLdNyIgAyzHxyQiAj5ND3ODbVTu3x-' target='_blank'>Required Examinations</a> Yale Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=-rGz4OcWLs_un1-7OOOOOOdvmc9KYFaHa7Lh9GtbaTX7SwIaCseo483oC2j5Fx-Nlfc8Th