dies）：为期4-7年（视论文完成情况），要求申请者本科毕业，拥有自然资源，如林学、生物学、化学、经济学或数学专业背景，要求递交GRE考试成绩，GRE Subject自愿递交。此外，学生在攻读PhD学位过程中，达到相关要求，也可获得MS或M.Phil学位*(4)(5)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=YrwF0vBtwQ4TaJV1UUUUUUkZWuwBGQgqxTPAi43vxfL_9fwqz4Evj8L0cI69TDsucW8T' target='_blank'>Cost of Attendance</a> Yale School of Forestry &amp; Environmental Studies</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQ1Owp7HocLWQQQQQQ91O7K3g6tA1bRlHcpejgsOm9Q6mU267Ogysx53WqoZy4Y-sgJ5Ga-5kFf8ObfHTnoLShDbD79OJZCyRQl' target='_blank'>Apply to Masters Program</a> Yale School of Forestry &amp; Environmental Studies</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=3rHk7mgRwySz718rI_gK1bzjYw9l0BgfoFKnhK_rFYRWOMb0BfsEQC4lzLh1FqAPgwH1MwkbNdW2OZL0byRmJOZPlVDmJtB0QKigZDeF7q7J' target='_blank'>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</a> Yale School of Forestry &amp; Environmental Studies</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTdnL9PXW0VB888881x4_e7oIzZM61MFMFnEEpICJnA_O983W062jhLVQwHa-VSv5lBVcjBcItmGCJxoB4W5HL6Kxf33B7yVQUjGNR_oBRqnfZqgrCDsECc6N9A6WIGjr73UDxRYt5kPCx47HhTxmw17mHl5f4eEZXsyur' target='_blank'>Graduate School of Arts and Sciences Programs and Policies 2015&ndash;2016</a> Yale University</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_29wZUg37Rg333333FKIF1JyrZGWOpbC_4d7ik7vc6Cvu-_xgbYmjlEzp-4dKQItOK0h5KhDboZRLdw4Zw7b89GT' target='_blank'>Degree Programs</a> Yale School of Forestry &amp; Environmental Studies</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJEIw0DYWaO0hhhhhh-1ZUdJfuiWg38p-tg9YsOZRoOp_xgbYmjlRoEA_saiHoEgYogi69Q3RoDf_AR9keNp-ArpYa4PiA46t' target='_blank'>One-Year Mid Career Masters</a> Yale School of Forestry &amp; Environmental Studies</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>法学院</h2><h3>JD项目</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.2%">			<p><a href='htt