ww.qianmu.org/LLM' target='_blank'>LLM</a>词条。</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nHVlwvLQzw6MHHHHHHFogx3Nb_TX1b2c2cjQEZ5WiaIMxGV_6f4_W8g3iqoNH0spYJaZAWtZOSikw_ikqRImPkxHlkCwGdBV0N' target='_blank'>Student Budget &amp; Cost of Attendance</a> Yale Law School,&nbsp;Yale University</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwaik0k8mhEtOOOOOOcgxYcP8B4mtzDODO8WmFA3DNthf1kYEJHYcRrxvHjlv3zlveMyfGMOwp2-RWv2bfHi-OPItmzhRXeN5EC' target='_blank'>LL.M. Requirements</a> Yale University</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbyf7LlbvUhhillllll7eK4sVpB03tmzqzqk1ZIpu45vnBEKl6oalEVbSWKVJWmMJvJhvHEhT7ZRzFEHgwSWSH7XKpL-HaW5nLmh0l5N' target='_blank'>Before You Apply for the LL.M.</a> Yale University</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=frh1ZE--kSyncF195NdbeMmIauvZsljCwP-2e35cRrwfcvTPc3TD6da9x0msIPE2dBY3rO-yGo_MPT0Ncc4qxCSO9Oe0tumgZG7AlaEPeo707Pp7CwP-x' target='_blank'>Steps in Applying for the LL.M. - Yale Law School</a>&nbsp;Yale University</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BYSk-uzkApxrrrrrrALXhlvPj48-H-HsUAy2vpzJuAOCUWOXI4O-RoOXboHdI4MdF_ZbMfaCcrL_tm' target='_blank'>LL.M. Admissions FAQ</a> Yale University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>其他项目</h3><p>耶鲁大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>法学</a>院（Yale Law School）成立于1843年，除开设有JD和LLM项目外，还开设有以下三种学位项目，分别是：*(1)</p><ul>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>法学</a>硕士（Master of Studies in Law，缩写：MSL）：为期1年，要求申请者博士毕业，拥有非法学专业背景*(2)</li>	<li>法理博士（Doctor of the Science of Law，缩写：JSD）：要求申请者拥有耶鲁大学法学院法学硕士（LLM）学位*(3)</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>法学</a>哲学博士（PhD in Law）：为期3年，要求申请者拥有美国大学法学博士（JD）学位*(4)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=frh1ZEiIw0DYWa2U222222EuQ4Ewiz361j1jCYB9Gw5nX_BPpYOPQx39XJgPsaSuXJm6T4OkoB0xop1cikhcLSRf9NjAir' target='_blank'>Degree Programs- Yale Law School</a>&nbsp;Yale University</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_3eLPImad0EXFnJzbaIJBeSD0XqkC2y0vnfh2IobrTJQtUystavHf-n2fpdw0ESqVsyEDGwtvU0EvHef-YmHkFUiGw-jlXqPD3h2xvMp8' target='_blank'>M.S.L. Application- Yale Law School</a>&nbsp;Yale University</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlEtLqEHvzTPxxxxxxpURY1CdUmcV-EQEQa_2ywzPfYh3LubU34boxTC5QLt5b8tYcnDFTQhstaGXI5KBy6DNiZgRxs0xBjHp6' target='_blank'>J.S.D. Application- Yale Law School</a>&nbsp;Yale University</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_1jk78ysUj9zvBHwo3yh2XvT9zUZEIHpgMqRtV6xxHbcCMNIL65qqCTYaCjWhf_GZ8cIFruRcMd7I7u8CYSEpWVRBUEi7' target='_blank'>PhD Program Frequently Asked Questions- Yale Law School</a>&nbsp;Yale University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>音乐学院</h2><p>耶鲁<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/音乐' target='_blank'>音乐</a>学院（Yale School of Music）成立于1894年，目前约有学生200名，提供各类专业学位（Professional Degree）教育。该学院的招收的学生，均为攻读音乐专业学位的研究生，本科生和PhD学生的招生和教育由耶鲁音乐系提供。</p><p>耶鲁音乐学院的教学注重室内音乐表演、听觉训练及合奏技能，同时兼重音乐史与音乐理论，除主修专业外，该学院的下的所有项目都非常注重上述四项的训练。</p><p>耶鲁音乐学院开设有五种学位项目，分别是：</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:177px">			<p><strong>学位项目</strong></p>			</td>			<td style="width:57px">			<p><strong>学制</strong></p>			</td>			<td style="width:123px">			<p><strong>专业背景要求</strong></p>			</td>			<td style="width:221px">			<p><strong>特点</strong></p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:177px">			<p>音乐硕士（Master of Music ,M.M.）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:57px">			<p>2年</p>			</td>			<td style="width:123px">			<p>本科以上学历</p>			</td>			<td style="width:221px">			<p>开设最广，攻读人数最多，耶鲁音乐学院70%的学生均为MM学生</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:177px">			<p>艺术家文凭（Artist Diploma ,A.D.）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:57px">			<p>2年</p>			</td>			<td style="width:123px">			<p>要求申请者已获音乐硕士学历</p>			</td>			<td style="width:221px">			<p>多数为已有工作经验的音乐从业人</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:177px">			<p>音乐博士（Doctor of Musical Arts ,D.M.A.）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:57px">			<p>5年</p>			</td>			<td style="width:123px">			<p>要求申请者已获音乐硕士学历</p>			</td>			<td style="width:221px">			<p>学生需先花2年时间在校学习，后续再需3年专业训练</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:177px">			<p>表演证书(Certificate in Performance)</p>			</td>			<td style="width:57px">			<p>3年</p>			</td>			<td style="width:123px">			<p>高中毕业</p>			</td>			<td style="width:221px">			<p>主要针对一些尚未获得学士学位的非常规申请者，一般年龄较小，音乐才华出众</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:177px">			<p>本硕连读(B.A./M.M.)</p>			</td>			<td style="width:57px">			<p>5年</p>			</td>			<td style="width:123px">			<p>耶鲁本科生</p>			</td>			<td style="width:221px">			<p>仅限耶鲁学院的本科在读学生</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(1)(2)(3)(4)(5)</p><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><p>耶鲁音乐学院的各项目的申请系通过该学院进行申请，申请者需指定自己想申请的专业及项目。每年的截止日期约在12月初，一般2月下旬出录取通知（如，2018年的申请截止日期为12月1日，第二年2月24出录取通知），必需有<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/个人作品' target='_blank'>个人作品</a>，必需参加<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/面试' target='_blank'>面试</a>，除作曲外，均无需<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GRE' target='_blank'>GRE</a>成绩。</p><p><strong>关于费用：</strong>学费全免，其余需由学生自己准备。*(6)</p><p><strong>申请材料</strong><strong>：</strong></p><p>（1）在线申请：Online Application</p><p>（2）申请费：$100 Application Fee</p><p>（3）个人作品： Prescreening Recordings</p><p>（4）<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/个人简历' target='_blank'>个人简历</a>：R&eacute;sum&eacute; or CV</p><p>（5）<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/推荐信' target='_blank'>推荐信</a>：3封</p><p>（6）<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/成绩单' target='_blank'>成绩单</a>：Academic Transcripts</p><p>（7）<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/TOEFL' target='_blank'>TOEFL</a>成绩：不低于86分，学生最晚需在第二年3月1日前达到该最低要求，机构编号：3992</p><p>（8）GRE：除作曲专业外，无需GRE成绩，机构编号：3992</p><p>（9）面试或试镜：一般在每年的2月第-3月中旬间举行，具体日期视专业不同而不同。*(1)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><ul>	<li>弦乐(Strings)	<ul>		<li>小提琴 (Violin)</li>		<li>中提琴 (Viola)</li>		<li>大提琴 (Cello)</li>		<li>低音提琴 (Double Bass)</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>管乐(Winds &amp; Brass)	<ul>		<li>长笛 (Flute)</li>		<li>双簧管 (Oboe)</li>		<li>单簧管 (Clarinet)</li>		<li>巴松管 (Bassoon)</li>		<li>号角 (Horn)</li>		<li>喇叭 (Trumpet)</li>		<li>长号 (Trombone)</li>		<li>图拔 (Tuba)</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>打击乐器 (Percussion)</li>	<li>竖琴 (Harp)</li>	<li>吉他 (Guitar)</li>	<li>钢琴 (Piano)</li>	<li>大键琴 (Harpsichord)</li>	<li>风琴(Organ)</li>	<li>声乐(Voice)	<ul>		<li>歌剧 (Opera)</li>		<li>早期声乐(Early Music Voice)</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>作曲(Composition)</li>	<li>音乐指挥(Conducting) *(7)</li></ul><p>注：早期声乐指的是一些古典的清唱、颂歌及宗教音乐类节目，该项目与耶鲁宗教音乐所设有联合项目。</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqV8VwAbLSI-dGGGGGGlogx3Nb_TXnPcjjpc3qvCb7xVk5DfARGpeNCqKDtUPyEUGQoBUQv_-DcsC_lsymZtLzjlF6' target='_blank'>Checklist of Required Application Materials</a>&nbsp;Yale School of Music</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlZjw2y6pnDz777777fpAb5PTjHRLDDPLNtRsNMKFmvhUbDRQe5-Ub3RweFZ7lnD3l7eup8D9ldDNW7e9Wnb9' target='_blank'>Degrees &amp; Programs-Master of Music</a>&nbsp;Yale School of Music</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=DroIGD45wfFe864hvvvvvvk_skcLmoIrZ7A33iAwdk95xjivlnnlngjPdQbtQK0lFG0hSsfM6sKE2w2fgw7lgBQoFUQ8F7Yl8b6jXrxi0x1QRwvZR' target='_blank'>Degrees &amp; Programs- Artist Diploma</a>&nbsp;Yale School of Music</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BY_kZqpfc6L4NnhoIPwbqs7w2z3O59ABNhSUsaeinVxNRWO8f1WPo3lx9pf_fLYGmpMsaDQRCwgx0ho7UwT4pPMupR-HXh0WpP_ft' target='_blank'>Degrees &amp; Programs- Doctor of Musical Arts</a>&nbsp;Yale School of Music</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=grPZ_x3cw1hiqn7F0zkiKlfwn0gDdKIz0KtfC2ZczZjMGC7U31YMvpwtlpOavvRBs6rBI88vYIhEhn99_EpyMhA19REBedhqnORekti16yv778q416yGb' target='_blank'>Degrees &amp; Programs- Certificate in Performance</a>&nbsp;Yale School of Music</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=arBPkMlik0k8mhEtOOOOOOxoZ5uSJofRNaXrrnX0or5e6sjTOHZfBQIjznmtOH2WzvKqg7pWJesZvjrBwuPCDJ' target='_blank'>Financial Aid</a>&nbsp;Yale School of Music</p><p>(7)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJ07kjzL8WHW3nGxoj3p2X0GR7PC33uNiWtS3BIwWju8kmOlkCDzTSm0CVHdMyRPpfzs-GuSPI5e89-6yCE3FJI5eTUrNsIqdqsUrtuI' target='_blank'>Degrees &amp; Programs- B.A./M.M.</a>&nbsp;Yale School of Music</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>护理学院</h2><p>耶鲁大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/护理' target='_blank'>护理</a>学院（Yale School of Nursing）成立于1923年，现设置有6种学位项目，除设置有专为拥有护理专业的背景学生设置的各类项目外，还有专为非护理专业背景的学生设置的项目，名为GEPN(Graduate Entry Prespecialty in Nursing)。*(1)</p><p>耶鲁护理学院是一个纯粹的专业研究生院，不招收本科学生，国家学生比例约为2%，现提供两种认证项目（已取消两种）：</p><ul>	<li>执业护士（Nurse Practitioner，缩写：NP）</li>	<li>助产资格护士（Certified Nurse Midwife，缩写：CNM）</li>	<li>临床护士专员（Clinical Nurse Specialist，缩写：CNS），已取消</li>	<li>认证<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/注册护士' target='_blank'>注册护士</a>麻醉师（Certified Registered Nurse Anesthetist，缩写：CRNA），已取消*(1)</li></ul><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:92px">			<p>项目名称</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>项目英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:66px">			<p>学制</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<p>专业背景要求</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:92px">			<p>护理硕士（GEPN）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>MSN for GEPN</p>			</td>			<td style="width:66px">			<p>3年</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>11月1日</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<ul>				<li>学士以上学历</li>			</ul>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:92px">			<p>护理硕士（RN）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>MSN for RNs</p>			</td>			<td style="width:66px">			<p>1-2年</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>2月1日</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<ul>				<li>需已拥有美国的注册护士资格</li>			</ul>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:92px">			<p>硕士后证书</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>Post-MSN Certificate</p>			</td>			<td style="width:66px">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>3月1日</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<ul>				<li>美国护理或同等学历</li>				<li>至少在1个州获得护士资格</li>				<li>1年以上临床护理经验</li>			</ul>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:92px">			<p>护理博士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>DNP Program</p>			</td>			<td style="width:66px">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>3月1日</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<ul>				<li>美国护理硕士或其同等学历</li>			</ul>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:92px">			<p>护理PhD</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>PhD in Nursing</p>			</td>			<td style="width:66px">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>1月2日</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<ul>				<li>美国护理硕士或其同等学历</li>			</ul>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:92px">			<p>博士后</p>			</td>			<td style="width:113px">			<p>Post-doc in Nursing</p>			</td>			<td style="width:66px">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>3月1日</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<ul>				<li>美国护理博士或其同等学历</li>			</ul>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(2)(3)</p><p>申请要求：</p><ul>	<li>TOEFL：总分不低于100分，单项口语不低于24分，其余不低于22分；</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/IELTS' target='_blank'>IELTS</a>：总分不低于7.0分，单项不低于6.5分；</li>	<li>硕士项目必需有GRE成绩，考试日期必需早于各自的申请截止日期；</li>	<li>除GEPN项目外，国际学生在入读耶鲁护理学院前，需先通过CGFNS（Commission on Graduates of Foreign Nursing Schools Examination）考试，不少项目还同时需获得美国注册护士（RN）的资格，具体请见上文的项目列表；</li>	<li>需递交3封推荐信；</li>	<li>GEPN学生申请时需指明自己欲攻读的专业。*(1)</li></ul><p><strong>费用与</strong><strong>奖学金</strong></p><p>耶鲁护理学院除PhD项目拥有全额<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>外，其余项目需经由护理学院的奖学金办公室申请。耶鲁护理学院的奖学金类型为Need-Blind，申请截止日期为2月1日。*(4)</p><p>关于学费：硕士项目，春季和秋季学期学费为$18,414/学期，夏季学期学费为$14,612/学期，合计一年学费约：$51,440。博士项目（DNP）春季和秋季学期学费为$12,241/学期。*(5)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>耶鲁护理学院硕士项目的临床专业方向如下：</p><ul>	<li>成年/老年急性护理执业护士（Adult/Gerontology Acute Care Nurse Practitioner）</li>	<li>家庭职业护士（Family Nurse Practitioner）</li>	<li>助产/女性健康护理执业护士（Nurse-Midwifery/Women&#39;s Health Nurse Practitioner）</li>	<li>护理管理、政策与领导（Nursing <a href='http://www.qianmu.org/管理学' target='_blank'>Management</a>, Policy and Leadership）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/儿科' target='_blank'>儿科</a>执业护士（Pediatric Nurse Practitioner）</li>	<li>精神科执业护士（Psychiatric-Mental Health Nursing）*(6)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=vrJH6YhhLa4bV_R1Z0DS1zwYnF35p36h1mUXS04EaMWtxXz6LahvkCsiT8rHZDghwAshjcn2S-TmtePS4903Mh-ON2N2xyt1JGmSsmdwpz_Ndp' target='_blank'>Frequently Asked Questions</a>&nbsp;Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQnHLdft_3MWLLLLLLq3tIjaBN_euB73zavJKoZYGmWtQPF7GfD7dcY9F-7Bz6uxoh7dqZrK95lGi8j_5NJd1XtF4' target='_blank'>Admissions Requirements for International Students</a>&nbsp;Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Trq48ptakAlE5zb9LLLLLLhVPdwKsXYbOjmK6I5feKES-7arqj3rzvh1yZw-yvx-cnhSy2RHrANSrvwXrZMXmDX-Fv3Rt2RarAEiFVr' target='_blank'>Graduate Entry Prespecialty in Nursing</a>&nbsp;Yale School of&nbsp;Nursing</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=CrXRF8CewqQ5MV4hvvvvvvVUu2GdY4qQ3FEdOSmLWdxlPeJ8zFV8uj-IrcMfJdNTPdSa0dSgrx' target='_blank'>Financial Aid</a>&nbsp;Yale School of&nbsp;Nursing</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=OrMxo-DyLx29RSLNMMMMiNNTXtru7-W_UTc57I4RqL7BPD6zsecYstZ_OtlR9nTjAdtcaQTYeF-tXZmoUVUaQHlo1tmoAr5zps' target='_blank'>Tuition, Special Fees, and Costs</a>&nbsp;Yale School of&nbsp;Nursing</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23qkkniNS4QQS0Yr0W3-HGeeyHoYDgyfj8nn_SHVFz0alPqxOQhKT-PgR7Nkab0PqDC6mTs3CVF2EQxI0Yl7dY46JX3bSalV0ByYDAo6' target='_blank'>Master&#39;s Program Specialties</a>&nbsp;Yale School of&nbsp;Nursing</p><h3>MSN项目</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:94px">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:54px">			<p>5</p>			</td>			<td style="width:84px">			<p>学费（/学期）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>$21,995</p>			</td>			<td style="width:103px">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:126px">			<p>11月1日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:94px">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:54px">			<p>100</p>			</td>			<td style="width:84px">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>3.4</p>			</td>			<td style="width:103px">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:126px">			<p>秋季</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:94px">			<p>IELTS要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:54px">			<p>7.0</p>			</td>			<td style="width:84px">			<p>GRE要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:104px">			<p>Required</p>			</td>			<td style="width:103px">			<p>GRE Subject</p>			</td>			<td style="width:126px">			<p>Not Required</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(1)(2)(3)(4)(5)</p><p>注：</p><p>（1）此处排名为<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/2020USNEWS%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%8A%A4%E7%90%86%E7%A1%95%E5%A3%AB%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D' target='_blank'>2020USNEWS美国护理硕士排名</a>*(1)</p><p>（2）此处为2019-2020学年护理硕士项目平均每学期的学费标准，此外，GEPN项目还需额外递交夏季学费的学费$17,450。需要注意的是，该费用每年会有较小（不超过5%）的涨幅*(2)</p><p>（3）此处的截止日期为MSN for RN项目的申请截止日期和MSN for GEPN项目申请截止日期*(3)</p><p>（4）TOEFL总分要求不低于100分，阅读、听力和写作均不低于22分，口语要求不低于24分；IELTS总分要求不低于7.0分，单项均不低于6.5分*(4)</p><p>（5）MSN项目并未设置最低GPA成绩，此处的GPA为争取Merit-based机会的前提</p><p>（6）MSN项目每年仅限秋季学期录取，秋季学期和春季学期课程时长16周，夏季学期较短，11周*(5)</p><p>（7）申请者优秀的GPA成绩并不能作为GRE豁免条件，但申请者如发表过高质量的论文或者期刊，学校可考虑豁免GRE成绩*(4)</p><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><p>耶鲁大学护理学院护理硕士项目（Master of Science in Nursing）包括有两个具体项目：</p><ul>	<li>GEPN项目（Master of Science in Nursing (MSN) for Graduate Entry Prespecialty in Nursing (GEPN) Program）：为期3年。要求申请者本科毕业，拥有非护理专业背景，无前置课程要求。申请者需在线递交申请，申请费100美金。符合初步录取条件的学生需参加学校组织的受邀面试，面试一般安排在1月底和2月初。该项目开设的课程以理论实践为主，提供实习。毕业生顺利毕业并取得护士执照后可继续攻读MSN学位。*(3)(6)(7)</li>	<li>MSN-RN项目（MSN for Registered Nurse (RN) Program）：要求申请者本科毕业，拥有护理相关专业背景。在申请时，满足护理专业资格评估并通过国际护理学校研究生委员会的认证。MSN项目每年仅限秋季学期录取，秋季学期和春季学期课程时长16周，夏季学期较短，11周。所有的申请者在录取前均需拥有康涅狄格州护士执照和专业医疗心肺复苏证书（CPR）。国际学生的成绩单需通过WES认证。符合初步录取条件的学生需参加学校组织的受邀面试，面试一般安排在3月。国际学生有机会获得学校提供的Merit-based奖学金。该项目开设的课程以临床为主，含三个研究方向：糖尿病护理（Diabetes Care Concentration）、成人肿瘤护理（Adult Oncology Concentration）和全球健康学（Global Health Concentration）。<strong>注：</strong>2018学年继续招收助产护理和女性健康项目。*(3)(7)(8)(9)(10) (11)(12)(13)</li></ul><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>耶鲁大学护理学院护理硕士项目开设的专业方向有：</p><ul>	<li>成人与老年医学急救护理实践（Adult/Gerontology Acute Care Nurse Practitioner Specialty）</li>	<li>成人与老年医学初级护理实践（Adult/Gerontology Primary Care Nurse Practitioner Specialty）</li>	<li>家庭护理实践（Family Nurse Practitioner Specialty）</li>	<li>助产护理与女性健康护理实践（Nurse-Midwifery/Women&#39;s Health Nurse Practitioner Specialty）</li>	<li>儿科护理实践（Pediatric Nurse Practitioner Specialty）</li>	<li>心理-精神健康护理（Psychiatric-Mental Health Nursing Specialty）*(14)</li></ul><p>参考资料：<a href='https://www.usnews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-nursing-schools/nur-rankings' target='_blank'>​</a></p><p>(1) <a href='https://www.usnews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-nursing-schools/nur-rankings' target='_blank'>Best Nursing Schools: Master&#39;s</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7P7kjzL8WqyhCtXAQRQYgjfe1qYBn_6Q-6hUShc-Zy623OqQkRFSmUgbcx4nmt3RYZgIIuu_IFUI9uH73OBJE_XswYttHhgAy8RHjWM5DzN32YjtzQUG3uY4EIFUICzkH0dH-amMDTh' target='_blank'>Tuition and Fees</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=SrWl9LTBLpMoTsZ_77777h3plP6qL459zbxqKQeogqCumrtH0bEHli5fmPYpRQkpmwCqSwiRqIrY7Lc8O2Y_qL6zUF4uODrYqIr3UTrYjDrzXDZbEqSxAogOYHm8eHzEVpm8eDlj' target='_blank'>Deadlines and Eligibility</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=grPZ_xnnkkP-GMnn77777lr71059d2IH-GFTh5EsYNV8nFMlxyL8W2c8AwT2Jzt4Hp1cST0IxOKIFaIBPvTCwZqWl5wQAzvfLXN0dWRlIa29ms0qUy_gl3_iloMV3uYB38S' target='_blank'>Required Exams</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHN7Gwx30hzElkkkkkkanr-2UyfBdKL4UY0scJU75pQ1zGLFzrOBcJhZzGM20Nk' target='_blank'>General Enrollment Information</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQL9kltmgRWTa1zF8p_oMuT6VTcY7vjOvWcQCt-X6jQWHRIUrNIJgeUOL-vVv9BR_63bu2aE3mciBaVcG3z6v6b1qP_9rW1c6RC3csbC1sZS_B4PHDmt6Pj6D1rdCWR_LX05XS-U8f-zeAxoCFTg' target='_blank'>GEPN</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(7)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=frh1ZEiuwN_n-hV1UUUUUUI07btTxCNRFtj4Cq8YreXrvKT74hKKWnUKFwGBbNZmFJvXxRQX40JXnj3eR6Jju4_PkhrsORLU5ija4DRUw2T' target='_blank'>Interviews</a>Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(8) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=_r75g1XxwGY_PVHbafVVNZf1UPJ65VwOXMGwBlKDBmNfeHe7xFvki1pYCVOdLV4_cCDh5FD7ddyEFZBY1ovuQhrio7adaQ1xOjFpRtD1uXvZm4y219MvGfN8Lzzv2_BxDaf_3S-NYu' target='_blank'>MSN</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(9) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCWAekvECxL9bvvvvvr3KWI7X392YRxDXH_kTsXza5ecGVxEGWF2O5_qG0BmK5_gUFsVv8rcZ83VUesZZ7poZFOdV8LoR7p8meGuc0Ed_kNVrRvw' target='_blank'>Curriculum</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(10) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIezt2-LUrJde5GzzzzzzRAN1MDVaz9ojrK-GaVq9dUQx1-C3tUj1VUiLra6cdwMTr3a19P' target='_blank'>General Enrollment Information</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(11) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aGbjk78ysq9bvvvvvrJ_MOX-yrwsjZUbwWlmLo1cJLKxaXzy5RXyvh1zm2E-ynxSA5Y3JUmSAbKcd3KRmCrx866jIw6d3_gJ7iY6yWi_VWs2hy8Llf_fxThRv_JRvLA8pc0B5N0nzFA3gm43iaI6wi' target='_blank'>Master&rsquo;s Program Concentrations</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(12) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=YrwF0vBrwMaU2rmQzzzzzztrGEi7zKg_1bRQTg_GJAC0lY7GrRvXAi7X65T