请说明</strong></p><p>耶鲁大学护理博士项目（Doctoral of Philosophy Program is Nursing）由耶鲁大学文理研究生院开设，以临床研究为主。为期4-7年，要求申请者本科毕业，拥有护理相关硕士学位背景，修读过统计学课程且GPA不低于3.0分。符合初步录取条件的学生需参加学校组织的受邀面试，具体可联系研究生院。所有录取的学生均可获得RA或TA奖学金。*(3)(5)(6)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>耶鲁大学护理博士项目开设的研究方向有：</p><ul>	<li>慢性疾病（例如糖尿病，肥胖心血管疾病，癌症，艾滋病毒/艾滋病，睡眠障碍）（chronic conditions (e.g., diabetes, obesity cardiovascular disease, cancer, HIV/AIDS, sleep disorders)）</li>	<li>疾病症状研究（symptoms）</li>	<li>自我与家庭管理（self- and family management）</li>	<li>妇幼保健（maternal and child health）</li>	<li>医疗保健政策（policy and politics of health care）</li>	<li>全球卫生（global health）</li>	<li>公平医疗与关怀弱势群体（health equity and care of vulnerable populations）</li>	<li>急性与重症监护（acute and critical care）</li>	<li>临终关怀（end-of-life and palliative care）</li>	<li>学校与社区医疗（school- and community-based interventions）*(7)</li>	<li>生物行为学实验室（Biobehavioral Laboratory）*(8)</li>	<li>急性与慢性病人睡眠障碍研究中心（Yale Center for Sleep Disturbance in Acute &amp; Chronic Conditions）*(9)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>在校学生列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=8rL6TCdPwYZ8xJncKML3dG1--ie0pLF1fdgay5C21EtKHylOAhI_TewIYuFWgy3LFh5hCngd1nOhdCIscwc_GB7q624ajZdCnnuIdgG14TNpYPLSzlKLbo0xeBKZE1E2QafoqYYWX14' target='_blank'>Current Students</a></li>	<li>研究列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BkFL6UOj4SeS-Gah8h5PlVFXFsqQBzVRiQShIL2KR56Brewoa-kTWwYF08Pm8ahNL1jGu6XhItmhRdMQqTj60' target='_blank'>Research</a></li>	<li>导师列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=xrVOpg_KkgdlWQxdswh96hY6wvFwKl3YdUIARne__3ga-XbBCU6Q72OFexm_T9teFz23G5LJfyKCCY6' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li>	<li>博士学生手册：<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/u/file/Yale%20phd_handbook_fall2016.pdf' target='_blank'>2016-17 PhD Handbook</a> (pdf)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23qrkQ2RhNsdNNNNN7vU8AKtb1_IgnCtk-wl9t2JyXfeGnYe8ctALH2feciueHoITaMXW9QODaF-n1rDL9F0eCKR41POD9QOECsZDaKqWaFq5CPq8bPwjn' target='_blank'>Required Exams</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/u/file/Yale%20phd_handbook_fall2016.pdf' target='_blank'>PhD Program Handbook</a>Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nHVjw2y6pFsuag9kSwdR_EWI8jmBTS9A7JX6F9XSoGoceFi82rkYW5BFdAxsfn6hpJV7oaq1z_5NzMcO1f8B4VapI2zgQW9yN6thpJZAoVHzfkSjcSvNUdEVxt-JfZ1xbLTFRLNzS52b' target='_blank'>Tuition and Fees</a>Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=erlnE6B6kBHWJpuF111111G82oW4Z0Dm3IK4vCNeB4fkRprnxIJn2qDsRCjnHMVi6EtaKJUXZhUXHf4R6j7nBhtXHjICKWAq-c' target='_blank'>PhD</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nHVawJr7tI5pbbbbbb9ARjDXMlLoyThXk_7tHX2Eu19UnTsURvLZujeA5_OAuP2XSPlt6XeZ5dkUi_T' target='_blank'>How to Apply</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibDJkIT16EtEggggggDCB-lhZcJOhnqe-RJBmjrnWa6CQHRWQzFWIko3lMzcGFAOi6EpeHOpqkxPAN8vbD-4COU-bT_semsgUy0TRhi' target='_blank'>Interviews</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(7) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=3rHk7m9WkqQ6K5hQwwwwwwiUshiU3dE-nhVs5NfZDMpM67N3iQesUh2s4o6P7TcLN_2HZoBn-jMQxxrH0ZPUydRn5FwK7TorzTsZ5L9Ai-c' target='_blank'>Fields of Study</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(8) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=zrQ-nH7iLOJkATPEvufTh1wluxl3aBlqQAZyYP1u-d83XhFaUrEu6R-JGIq1gkZ_oduSyqbdO7gm-s8CJzS7zrduLco-8ESjV-YrPG8rdetuTFGyqzWI6' target='_blank'>BBL</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>(9) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=OrMxo-6Bk6RIqAfCAAAAABwH2fVzi5M7hnqe-RJBm6h5MGj1-x1VwP1VQZzLBS598vh_bTOzYTe3YFATelA3cSrjgYsj-NuZiBTxClDmslTsnITYrzFnhSmDx9sLa0pIm-fZfBXejBQZxPH0yPQjlGvdy_-V1kgKycZFOo4PxWyZjT3HUvjC_XJIUhOF_8R9' target='_blank'>SDACC</a> Yale School of Nursing</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>艺术学院</h2><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadd